						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone lying in Survey No. 1.</hi></p>						

						<p>Gōvinda III—(Undated).</p>						

						<p>This damaged inscription referring itself to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Prabhūtavarsha,</hi> records the death of a hero (name lost). A certain <hi rend="bold">Kauṇḍala</hi> is mentioned. On the grounds of palaeography the king may be identified with <hi rend="bold">Gōvinda III.</hi></p>						

